Also when i try on other computers it wont work there either, im doing something wrong, im pretty sure about it. Can any of you guys help me or teamview me or anything? If any of you guys can help me and fix it, i will gladly give them co, admin or mod :) Here's a pic of the portforwarding i tried: http://i1086.photobucket.com/albums/j460/Darkermans/router.png Please help:) Thanks guys:) :D
